```class Solution {
    public int numberOfSubstrings(String s) {
        int count = 0, a = 0, b = 0, c = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {
            if (s.charAt(i) == 'a') a++;
            else if (s.charAt(i) == 'b') b++;
            else c++;
            if (a > 0 && b > 0 && c > 0) count++;
        }
        return count;
    }
}```
